            <p class="rewards-use__text">
                If you have enough points to redeem, simply apply your points for a discount at checkout with the drop
                down menu!
            </p>

            <h5 class="h5-title rewards-use__subtitle">
                You can redeem in 100 point increments
            </h5>

            <ul class="rewards-use__list">
                <li>
                    <h3 class="h3-title">10$</h3>
